      "description": "Auto-synced Ψ constants: 0.001=gate_micro, 0.002=soc_ema_glacial, 0.005=verify_v2_variance_min, 0.008=soc_ema_slow, 0.01=verify_v4_monotonic_tolerance, 0.012=bio_noise_base, 0.014=alpha, 0.02=verify_v1_std_cos_min, 0.03=kuramoto_amplitude, 0.04=phi_feedback_strength (+24 more)",
